{"tid":1060561,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拜仁CEO路明尼加出言嘲諷祖記重金買C朗：一切都是Marketing","createTime":"2019-03-13T22:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T00:06:09.000Z","uid":25345,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"211fd9e9cdb28b60de0147a3e8e91389fb40906e","tid":1060561,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:19:55.000Z","msg":"拜仁CEO說，看到C朗以天價轉會去祖記令到他很驚喜，但換轉是拜仁一定不會花這麼大筆金錢去買入C朗拿度：「拜仁一定不會為一個33歲的球員花這麼多錢。很明顯，這宗交易是Marketing成份佔了很高比重。看到現在的情況，大家都見到C朗去意甲引來很多關注，這一點我非常理解。C朗是一位過去幾年在皇馬贏盡一切的球星，也是5屆金球獎得主，是一位偉大的足球員。」"},{"pid":"d3095b4d601da3dfc5a8ce5478359ce7782bf813","tid":1060561,"uid":73952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:20:57.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"36f6c52a27f52d86a2b68f6e2f12c7dde4c1d855","tid":1060561,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:21:43.000Z","msg":"朗迷咪撚咁小氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連拜仁都jer埋"},{"pid":"5170f2524f94ae778a30eb7b055228a814300eca","tid":1060561,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373cd03460b75723a8ebbfa1c19b95bd8066e614","tid":1060561,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:36:53.000Z","msg":"講得唔啱咩"},{"pid":"bf502be67f9cae239fe8857fda0577efd95e01c7","tid":1060561,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:38:17.000Z","msg":"Marketing球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d74148b56e2feead70a3cce498534be6300b60","tid":1060561,"uid":201601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:46:42.000Z","msg":"條廢老都幾肉酸<br />\n前排特登開個記者會去屌9記者<br />\nbernat走咗之後又公開屌9佢廢"},{"pid":"838b2efd98f0c3b4c2f2da43e26c713f22cb2110","tid":1060561,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d74148b56e2feead70a3cce4